      <action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="M001187">Mr. Meadows</sponsor> (for himself, <cosponsor name-id="C001047">Mrs. Capito</cosponsor>, <cosponsor name-id="M001191">Mr. Murphy of Florida</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="B001251">Mr. Butterfield</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HBA00">Committee on Financial Services</committee-name>
